text: Francisco Guillermo Cumplido Cereceda (23 October 1930 â€“ 16 July 2022) was a Chilean politician and lawyer. He was the Minister of Justice under Patricio Aylwin's government from 1990 to 1994. He was a member of the Christian Democratic Party. Cumplido was born in Santiago, Chile. Cumplido died on 16 July 2022 in Santiago at the age of 91. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Chilean lawyers Category:Politicians from Santiago
